commit.message:
Fix NICOLA key pairing

Do not pair thumb key and normal key just because they are pressed at the same time.
But pair the keys whose MAKE events are neighboring in time series.
For example, two sequences below should make the same results:
- K make, Thumb-R make, D make, and all break
- Thumb-R make, K make, D make, and all break

Fix NICOLA voicing

Combine kana and successing voiced consonant mark.

Fix the format of layout definition files with text-arrays

Text-array separator is not white space but comma.

Add support for building with anthy-unicode

Fix #12
